ive_case\" title=\"accusative case\">Accusative</a>\n</th>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la acc|s-form-of origin-pecus\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/pecudem#Latin\" title=\"pecudem\">pecudem</a></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la acc|p-form-of origin-pecus\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/pecudes#Latin\" title=\"pecudes\">pecud&#x113;s</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"case-header\"><a href=\"/wiki/ablative_case\" title=\"ablative case\">Ablative</a>\n</th>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la abl|s-form-of origin-pecus\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/pecude#Latin\" title=\"pecude\">pecude</a></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la abl|p-form-of origin-pecus\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/pecudibus#Latin\" title=\"pecudibus\">pecudibus</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"case-header\"><a href=\"/wiki/vocative_case\" title=\"vocative case\">Vocative</a>\n</th>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la voc|s-form-of origin-pecus\" lang=\"la\"><strong class=\"selflink\">pecus</strong></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la voc|p-form-of origin-pecus\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/pecudes#Latin\" title=\"pecudes\">pecud&#x113;s</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table><h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Hypernyms\">Hypernyms</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=pecus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: Hypernyms\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h4><ul><li><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content qualifier-content\">larger livestock</span><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">)</span><span class=\"ib-colon sense-qualifier-colon\">:</span> <span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/pecus#Latin\" title=\"pecus\">pecus</a></span><